#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:25
msgid ""
"Stable identity of this MP server. Used as the coordinator membership key"
" and projected onto the OTel ``service.instance.id`` resource attribute "
"on every metric and span (so telemetry and coordinator membership share "
"one id). When the flag is not passed, defaults to a random UUID v4 minted"
" at startup."
msgstr ""
"此 MP 服务器的稳定身份。用作协调器成员资格密钥，并在每个指标和跨度上投影到 OTel ``service.instance.id`` "
"资源属性（因此遥测和协调器成员资格共享一个 ID）。当未传递该标志时，默认为在启动时生成的随机 UUID v4。"

