msgstr "``256``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:39
msgid "Chunk size for KV cache operations (in tokens)."
msgstr "KV Cache 操作的块大小（以 token 为单位）。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:40
msgid "``--max-workers``"
msgstr "``--max-workers``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:41
msgid "``1``"
msgstr "``1``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:42
msgid ""
"Base number of worker threads. Sets the default for both the GPU "
"(affinity) pool and the CPU (normal) pool. Can be overridden per-pool "
"with ``--max-gpu-workers`` and ``--max-cpu-workers``."
msgstr ""
"工作线程的基本数量。为 GPU（亲和性）池和 CPU（正常）池设置默认值。可以通过 ``--max-gpu-workers`` 和 "
"``--max-cpu-workers`` 针对每个池进行覆盖。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:45
msgid "``--max-gpu-workers``"
msgstr "``--max-gpu-workers``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:46 ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:51
msgid "(inherits ``--max-workers``)"
msgstr "(继承 ``--max-workers``)"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:47
msgid ""
"Worker threads for the GPU affinity pool (STORE/RETRIEVE). Requests from "
"the same vLLM instance are always dispatched to the same thread, "
"eliminating GPU transfer lock contention."
msgstr "用于 GPU 亲和力池（存储/检索）的工作线程。来自同一 vLLM 实例的请求始终分配到同一线程，从而消除 GPU 传输锁争用。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:50
msgid "``--max-cpu-workers``"
msgstr "``--max-cpu-workers``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:52
msgid "Worker threads for the normal CPU pool (LOOKUP, etc.)."
msgstr "正常 CPU 池（查找等）的工作线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:53
msgid "``--hash-algorithm``"
msgstr "``--hash-algorithm``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:54
msgid "``blake3``"
msgstr "``blake3``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:55
msgid ""
"Hash algorithm for token-based operations. Choices: ``builtin``, "
"``sha256_cbor``, ``blake3``."
msgstr "基于令牌的操作的哈希算法。可选项：``builtin``、``sha256_cbor``、``blake3``。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:57
msgid "``--engine-type``"
msgstr "``--engine-type``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:58 ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:312
#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:320
msgid "``default``"
msgstr "``default``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:59
msgid ""
"Cache engine backend type. ``default`` uses standard prefix caching; "
"``blend`` selects the current CacheBlend V3 implementation (composes a "
"``BlendV3Module`` into the engine); ``blend_legacy`` selects the original"
" CacheBlend (composes a ``BlendModule``). Both blend variants require "
"``--supported-transfer-mode`` to be ``lmcache_driven`` or ``auto``. "
"Choices: ``default``, ``blend``, ``blend_legacy``."
msgstr ""
"缓存引擎后端类型。``default`` 使用标准前缀缓存；``blend`` 选择当前的 CacheBlend V3 实现（将 "
"``BlendV3Module`` 组合到引擎中）；``blend_legacy`` 选择原始的 CacheBlend（将 "
"``BlendModule`` 组合到引擎中）。这两种 blend 变体都需要 ``--supported-transfer-mode`` 设置为"
" ``lmcache_driven`` 或 "
"``auto``。可选项：``default``、``blend``、``blend_legacy``。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:66
msgid "``--supported-transfer-mode``"
msgstr "``--supported-transfer-mode``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:67 ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:452
msgid "``auto``"
msgstr "``auto``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:68
msgid ""
"Which worker → server transfer paths the server loads. ``lmcache_driven``"
" enables only the server-driven transfer path (STORE/RETRIEVE, supports "
"both CUDA IPC and CPU SHM); ``engine_driven`` enables only the non-GPU "
"(PREPARE/COMMIT) transfer path; ``auto`` (default) loads both so workers "
"of either device type can connect without manual configuration. Choices: "
"``lmcache_driven``, ``engine_driven``, ``auto``."
msgstr ""
"服务器加载的工作进程 → 服务器传输路径。 ``lmcache_driven`` 仅启用服务器驱动的传输路径（STORE/RETRIEVE，支持 "
"CUDA IPC 和 CPU SHM）； ``engine_driven`` 仅启用非 GPU（PREPARE/COMMIT）传输路径； "
"``auto``（默认）加载两者，以便任一设备类型的工作进程可以在无需手动配置的情况下连接。 选项： ``lmcache_driven``， "
"``engine_driven``， ``auto``。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:76
msgid "``--runtime-plugin-locations``"
msgstr "``--runtime-plugin-locations``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:77 ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:88
msgid "``[]``"
msgstr "``[]``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:78
msgid ""
"Zero or more paths to runtime plugin scripts or directories to launch "
"alongside the server. Plugins are spawned by ``MPRuntimePluginLauncher`` "
"and receive the full server config via the "
"``LMCACHE_RUNTIME_PLUGIN_CONFIG`` environment variable."
msgstr ""
"零个或多个路径，用于运行时插件脚本或目录，以便与服务器一起启动。插件由 ``MPRuntimePluginLauncher`` 生成，并通过 "
"``LMCACHE_RUNTIME_PLUGIN_CONFIG`` 环境变量接收完整的服务器配置。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:82
msgid "``--runtime-plugin-config``"
msgstr "``--runtime-plugin-config``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:83
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``\"{}\"``"
msgstr "``\"{}\"``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:84
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"JSON string of extra key-value config forwarded to runtime plugins via "
"``LMCACHE_RUNTIME_PLUGIN_EXTRA_CONFIG``. Example: "
"``'{\"plugin.frontend.heartbeat_url\": "
"\"http://localhost:5000/heartbeat\"}'``."
msgstr ""
"通过 ``LMCACHE_RUNTIME_PLUGIN_EXTRA_CONFIG`` 转发到运行时插件的额外键值配置的 JSON "
"字符串。示例：``'{\\\"plugin.frontend.heartbeat_url\\\": "
"\\\"http://localhost:5000/heartbeat\\\"}'``。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:87
msgid "``--script-allowed-imports``"
msgstr "``--script-allowed-imports``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:89
msgid ""
"Space-separated list of Python module names that scripts posted to the "
"HTTP ``/run_script`` endpoint are allowed to import. Example: ``--script-"
"allowed-imports numpy pandas``."
msgstr ""
"允许在 HTTP ``/run_script`` 端点发布的脚本导入的以空格分隔的 Python 模块名称列表。示例：``--script-"
"allowed-imports numpy pandas``。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:92
msgid "``--shm-name``"
msgstr "``--shm-name``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:93 ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:211
msgid "*(not set)*"
msgstr "*(未设置)*"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:94
msgid ""
"SHM segment name for non-GPU KV transfer (only used when the non-GPU path"
" is loaded, i.e. ``--supported-transfer-mode`` is ``auto`` or "
"``engine_driven``). Not set (default): auto-allocate a shared-memory "
"pool. ``\"\"`` (empty string): disable SHM and force the pickle transfer "
"path.  Any other value: use that exact name for the SHM pool segment."
msgstr ""
"非 GPU KV 传输的 SHM 段名称（仅在加载非 GPU 路径时使用，即 ``--supported-transfer-mode`` 为 "
"``auto`` 或 ``engine_driven``）。未设置（默认）：自动分配一个共享内存池。 ``\\\"\\\"``（空字符串）：禁用 "
"SHM 并强制使用 pickle 传输路径。 任何其他值：将该确切名称用于 SHM 池段。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:101
msgid "``--worker-reap-timeout-seconds``"
msgstr "``--worker-reap-timeout-seconds``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:102
msgid "``120.0``"
msgstr "``120.0``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:103
msgid ""
"Silence budget (seconds) after which a worker that has sent at least one "
"heartbeat PING but then gone quiet has its KV cache registration reaped, "
"freeing the leaked GPU context and CUDA IPC handles. ``0`` disables "
"reaping. Keep this at least 3x the engine adapter's "
"``lmcache.mp.heartbeat_interval`` (default 10s) so a few missed pings "
"never reap a live worker; the adapter warns at startup if its interval is"
" raised without raising this."
msgstr ""
"在发送至少一个心跳 PING 后静默的工作线程的沉默预算（秒），此时将收回其 KV Cache 注册，释放泄漏的 GPU 上下文和 CUDA "
"IPC 句柄。``0`` 禁用收回。保持此值至少为引擎适配器的 ``lmcache.mp.heartbeat_interval`` 的 3 "
"倍（默认 10 秒），以确保几次丢失的 PING 不会收回一个活跃的工作线程；如果在不提高此值的情况下提高其间隔，适配器在启动时会发出警告。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:110
msgid "``--worker-registration-grace-seconds``"
msgstr "``--worker-registration-grace-seconds``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:111
msgid "``3600.0``"
msgstr "``3600.0``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:112
msgid ""
"Silence budget (seconds) for a worker that registered but has never sent "
"a PING (still warming up, or died before its first request). Must be >= "
"``--worker-reap-timeout-seconds``. Generous by default so slow model "
"warmup is never mistaken for a dead worker."
msgstr ""
"为注册但从未发送 PING 的工作线程（仍在预热或在首次请求之前死亡）设置的沉默预算（秒）。必须大于或等于 ``--worker-reap-"
"timeout-seconds``。默认值宽松，以确保慢模型预热不会被误认为是死工作线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:116
msgid "``--enable-segmented-prefix``"
msgstr "``--enable-segmented-prefix``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:117
msgid "``False``"
msgstr "``False``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:118
msgid ""
"CacheBlend (``--engine-type blend``) only: on a mid-prefix L2 retrieve "
"failure, retain the gapped prefix so the post-gap chunks stay L1-resident"
" and only the dropped gap is recomputed, instead of truncating the prefix"
" at the gap. No effect for other engines. See "
":doc:`/mp/l2_storage/fault_inject` for a way to exercise it."
msgstr "CacheBlend (``--engine-type blend``) 仅适用：在中间前缀 L2 检索失败时，保留缺口前缀，以便缺口后的块保持在 L1 中驻留，只有丢失的缺口被重计算，而不是在缺口处截断前缀。对其他引擎没有影响。有关如何使用它，请参见 :doc:`/mp/l2_storage/fault_inject`。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:125
msgid "Lookup Hash Logging"
msgstr "查找哈希日志记录"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:127
msgid "Source: ``lmcache/v1/mp_observability/subscribers/logging/lookup_hash.py``"
msgstr "源: ``lmcache/v1/mp_observability/subscribers/logging/lookup_hash.py``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:129
msgid ""
"When enabled, the server publishes chunk hashes computed during "
"``lookup()`` as ``MP_LOOKUP`` events on the EventBus.  The "
"``LookupHashLoggingSubscriber`` writes these to rotating JSONL files for "
"offline analysis.  Disabled by default.  These arguments are part of the "
"Observability group."
msgstr ""
"启用时，服务器将在 EventBus 上发布在 ``lookup()`` 期间计算的块哈希作为 ``MP_LOOKUP`` 事件。 "
"``LookupHashLoggingSubscriber`` 将这些写入旋转的 JSONL 文件以供离线分析。 默认情况下禁用。 "
"这些参数是可观察性组的一部分。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:142
msgid "``--lookup-hash-log-dir``"
msgstr "``--lookup-hash-log-dir``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:143
msgid "``\"\"`` (disabled)"
msgstr "``\"\"`` (禁用)"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:144
msgid ""
"Directory to write lookup hash JSONL files. An empty string disables "
"logging."
msgstr "写入查找哈希 JSONL 文件的目录。空字符串将禁用日志记录。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:146
msgid "``--lookup-hash-log-rotation-interval``"
msgstr "``--lookup-hash-log-rotation-interval``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:147
msgid "``21600`` (6 h)"
msgstr "``21600`` (6 小时)"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:148
msgid "Time interval in seconds before rotating to a new log file."
msgstr "在切换到新日志文件之前的时间间隔（以秒为单位）。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:149
msgid "``--lookup-hash-log-rotation-max-size``"
msgstr "``--lookup-hash-log-rotation-max-size``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:150
msgid "``104857600`` (100 MB)"
msgstr "``104857600`` (100 MB)"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:151
msgid ""
"Max file size in bytes before rotating even if the time interval has not "
"elapsed."
msgstr "在时间间隔尚未到达之前，旋转前的最大文件大小（以字节为单位）。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:153
msgid "``--lookup-hash-log-max-files``"
msgstr "``--lookup-hash-log-max-files``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:154
msgid "``100``"
msgstr "``100``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:155
msgid ""
"Max number of log files to keep.  Oldest files are deleted when this "
"limit is exceeded."
msgstr "保留的最大日志文件数量。当超过此限制时，最旧的文件将被删除。"

