#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:180
msgid "L1 Memory Manager"
msgstr "L1 内存管理器"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:182 ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:223
#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:251 ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:270
#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:302
msgid "Source: ``lmcache/v1/distributed/config.py``"
msgstr "来源: ``lmcache/v1/distributed/config.py``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:191
msgid "``--l1-size-gb``"
msgstr "``--l1-size-gb``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:192 ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:280
msgid "*required*"
msgstr "*必需*"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:193
msgid ""
"Size of the L1 tier in GB. Sizes the pinned-DRAM L1 by default, or the "
"GDS slab file when ``--gds-l1-path`` is set (see *GDS L1 Tier* below)."
msgstr ""
"L1 层的大小（以 GB 为单位）。默认情况下，设置固定 DRAM 的 L1 大小，或者在设置了 ``--gds-l1-path`` 时，设置 "
"GDS 块文件（请参见下面的 *GDS L1 层*）。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:195
msgid "``--l1-use-lazy`` / ``--no-l1-use-lazy``"
msgstr "``--l1-use-lazy`` / ``--no-l1-use-lazy``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:196 ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:244
msgid "``True``"
msgstr "``True``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:197
msgid ""
"Enable or disable lazy allocation for L1 memory. Pass ``--l1-use-lazy`` "
"to enable (default) or ``--no-l1-use-lazy`` to explicitly disable. Lazy "
"allocation relies on ``cudart`` host-pinned memory, so on non-CUDA "
"backends (where ``lmcache.torch_dev`` exposes no ``cudart`` attribute) it"
" is automatically downgraded to eager allocation with a logged warning, "
"regardless of the flag value."
msgstr ""
"启用或禁用 L1 内存的延迟分配。传递 ``--l1-use-lazy`` 以启用（默认）或 ``--no-l1-use-lazy`` "
"以显式禁用。延迟分配依赖于 ``cudart`` 主机固定内存，因此在非 CUDA 后端（其中 ``lmcache.torch_dev`` 不暴露"
" ``cudart`` 属性）时，它会自动降级为急切分配，并记录警告，无论标志值如何。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:204
msgid "``--l1-init-size-gb``"
msgstr "``--l1-init-size-gb``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:205
msgid "``20``"
msgstr "``20``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:206
msgid "Initial allocation size (GB) when using lazy allocation."
msgstr "使用延迟分配时的初始分配大小（GB）。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:207
msgid "``--l1-align-bytes``"
msgstr "``--l1-align-bytes``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:208
msgid "``4096``"
msgstr "``4096``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:209
msgid "Alignment size in bytes (default 4 KB)."
msgstr "对齐大小（以字节为单位，默认 4 KB）。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:210
msgid "``--l1-devdax-path``"
msgstr "``--l1-devdax-path``"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:212
msgid ""
"Optional ``/dev/dax*`` device or mmap-able file to use as the L1 backing "
"arena.  When set, disable lazy allocation with ``--no-l1-use-lazy`` and "
"disable SHM transfer advertising with ``--shm-name \"\"`` because the L1 "
"bytes live in the DAX mapping.  If a DAX L2 adapter with the same "
"``device_path`` is registered, that adapter's ``max_dax_size_gb`` is used"
" as the L1 Device-DAX overflow size."
msgstr "可选的 ``/dev/dax*`` 设备或可 mmap 的文件，用作 L1 后备区域。当设置时，使用 ``--no-l1-use-lazy`` 禁用延迟分配，并使用 ``--shm-name \\\"\\\"`` 禁用 SHM 传输广告，因为 L1 字节存在于 DAX 映射中。如果注册了具有相同 ``device_path`` 的 DAX L2 适配器，则该适配器的 ``max_dax_size_gb`` 将用作 L1 Device-DAX 溢出大小。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:221
msgid "GDS L1 Tier"
msgstr "GDS L1 层"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:225
msgid ""
"Opt-in. Setting ``--gds-l1-path`` switches the L1 medium from pinned DRAM"
" to an NVMe slab file accessed via GPUDirect Storage (cuFile DMA). The "
"CPU pinned-DRAM tier is then disabled, and ``--l1-size-gb`` sizes the "
"slab. Disable byte-array L2 adapters when this is on (the GDS tier "
"exposes no L1 memory buffer for them to register)."
msgstr ""
"选择加入。设置 ``--gds-l1-path`` 将 L1 媒介从固定 DRAM 切换到通过 GPUDirect Storage (cuFile"
" DMA) 访问的 NVMe 块文件。然后禁用 CPU 固定 DRAM 层，并且 ``--l1-size-gb`` "
"设置块的大小。当此选项开启时，禁用字节数组 L2 适配器（GDS 层不为它们注册提供 L1 内存缓冲区）。"

#: ../../source/mp/configuration.rst:238
msgid "``--gds-l1-path``"
msgstr "``--gds-l1-path``"

